OL,3,CHundreds of jobs saved after buyer
OL,4,Cfound for private ambulance service
OL,6,FHundreds of jobs have been saved after
OL,7,Fa private ambulance company which
OL,8,Fprovides services to the NHS and
OL,9,Ftransport for patients was saved from
OL,10,Fclosure.
OL,12,FBristol Ambulance had been at risk of
OL,13,Fcollapse over an alleged #1million
OL,14,Funpaid tax bill, with service users
OL,15,Fadvised to find alternative ways to
OL,16,Ftravel.
