OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779804668
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs saved after buyer
OL,4,Cfound for private ambulance service
OL,6,FIt has now been bought by national
OL,7,Fhealthcare transport company EMED
OL,8,FGroup and a estimated 315 staff, 120
OL,9,Fambulances and seven depots will be
OL,10,Ftransferred as part of the agreement.
OL,12,FBristol Ambulance does not provide
OL,13,Femergency services but transports
OL,14,Fvulnerable patients to and from
OL,15,Fappointments and provides medical
OL,16,Fcover for events in the South West.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
