OL,3,CHundreds of jobs saved after buyer
OL,4,Cfound for private ambulance service
OL,6,FNew owners EMED Group said services
OL,7,Fwill continue on a "business-as-usual
OL,8,Fbasis" and advised patients to
OL,9,Fcontinue booking transport and
OL,10,Fattending appointments unless advised
OL,11,Fotherwise.
OL,13,F"Our priority throughout this process
OL,14,Fhas been protecting continuity of
OL,15,Fservice for patients and supporting
OL,16,Four colleagues across the
OL,17,Forganisation," said Rob Johnson, CEO
OL,18,Fat Bristol Ambulance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
