OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779804668
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs saved after buyer
OL,4,Cfound for private ambulance service
OL,6,F"EMED have demonstrated a clear
OL,7,Fcommitment to maintaining services,
OL,8,Fsupporting teams and working closely
OL,9,Fwith NHS partners during the
OL,10,Ftransition period."
OL,12,FHe also thanked Bristol Ambulance's
OL,13,Fworkforce for their "professionalism,
OL,14,Fresilience and continued dedication to
OL,15,Fpatient care" throughout the period of
OL,16,Funcertainty over the company's future.
